WEBVTT

01:34.360 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

02:17.240 --> 02:18.320
Water.

02:22.240 --> 02:23.480
Thanks.

02:26.720 --> 02:27.560
What happened to your hand?

02:46.920 --> 02:48.040
Who are you?

02:49.360 --> 02:50.880
Tell me. Who are you?

02:56.040 --> 02:58.080
Who are you? Tell me. Who are you?

03:01.400 --> 03:03.280
Mom. Dad. Mom!

03:03.800 --> 03:05.160
What? What's wrong?

03:05.240 --> 03:07.040
Jiang was eating there at night
instead of sleeping.

03:07.120 --> 03:07.960
She scared me.

03:08.040 --> 03:09.760
What are you doing?

03:09.840 --> 03:11.880
Why are you acting weird
in the middle of the night?

03:11.960 --> 03:13.880
Do you want to scare our family to death?

03:13.960 --> 03:15.680
Are you stealing rice?

03:15.760 --> 03:17.520
Didn't I feed you enough during the day?

03:19.320 --> 03:20.560
- Mom.
- Son.

03:21.200 --> 03:22.320
Are you scared?

03:22.400 --> 03:23.400
I'm afraid.

03:23.480 --> 03:24.760
Don't be afraid. It's okay.

03:24.840 --> 03:26.640
Go back to your room and sleep.

03:32.320 --> 03:33.160
I bumped into something by accident.

03:39.480 --> 03:40.920
If you have something on your mind,
why don't you say it?

03:42.880 --> 03:43.880
I don't.

03:43.960 --> 03:45.840
I just bumped into something.

03:49.280 --> 03:50.800
It's time for the art exam.

03:51.520 --> 03:52.880
Take care of yourself.

03:54.960 --> 03:55.960
I will.

04:18.640 --> 04:19.920
What are you doing?

04:39.120 --> 04:40.520
I'm painting a wing.

04:41.840 --> 04:44.200
Later, the scars will fly away.

04:53.320 --> 04:54.520
Does it look good?

05:01.080 --> 05:02.200
Yes.

05:34.520 --> 05:35.680
3,139 DAYS

05:36.640 --> 05:41.840
DAY 77 OF LIVING TOGETHER OFFICIALLY

05:54.920 --> 05:56.800
Why isn't the chair by the door?

06:01.360 --> 06:02.680
Was I sleepwalking again?

06:12.400 --> 06:13.240
Morning.

06:31.560 --> 06:32.840
Did I…

06:33.960 --> 06:34.840
sleepwalk yesterday?

06:48.880 --> 06:51.920
Did I do anything inappropriate?

06:58.440 --> 06:59.840
Didn't I tell you last time?

06:59.920 --> 07:01.520
When you see me sleepwalking again,

07:01.600 --> 07:02.480
just pretend you didn't see me.

07:02.560 --> 07:03.600
I haven't said anything yet.

07:03.680 --> 07:04.800
You are rushing
to distance yourself from me?

07:04.880 --> 07:06.880
I'm not.

07:06.960 --> 07:07.960
I wanted to remind you.

07:08.920 --> 07:10.080
Want it?

07:13.160 --> 07:14.000
Okay.

07:20.520 --> 07:22.760
What did I do yesterday?

07:24.480 --> 07:25.880
Were you still up at that hour?

07:25.960 --> 07:27.120
Yes.

07:29.360 --> 07:31.880
Did I really do something inappropriate?

07:38.560 --> 07:41.040
You didn't do what you did before, but…

07:42.800 --> 07:44.120
you did something much worse.

07:57.680 --> 07:58.600
Did I do something?

07:59.280 --> 08:01.080
Don't think about those impure things.

08:03.800 --> 08:05.400
So, what did I do?

08:07.520 --> 08:08.600
I won't be specific.

08:08.680 --> 08:09.960
I'm afraid that when I'm done,
you'll be devastated

08:10.560 --> 08:12.920
and unable to believe
that you could do such a thing.

08:14.400 --> 08:15.280
You're welcome.

08:15.360 --> 08:17.480
I'm just sweet and forgiving.

08:17.560 --> 08:19.880
But you can tell me. I can take it.

08:23.400 --> 08:24.600
Forget it. I can't say it.

08:24.680 --> 08:27.480
What would make a person
of your character unable to say it?

08:27.560 --> 08:29.800
Let me put it this way.
I've been in a good mood lately,

08:29.880 --> 08:32.280
so I'll let you off the hook
for now, but later,

08:32.919 --> 08:36.120
I'll make you repay me little by little.

08:36.200 --> 08:37.559
Then, can I repay now?

08:37.640 --> 08:39.159
Now is not the time.

08:40.280 --> 08:41.480
How will I repay?

08:43.760 --> 08:46.280
Repay with money?

08:55.360 --> 08:58.280
Can I write you a note first?

08:58.360 --> 08:59.960
Because I haven't gotten my paycheck yet.

09:04.400 --> 09:05.560
And if it happens again,

09:05.640 --> 09:08.240
you can hit me to wake me up.

09:12.440 --> 09:13.400
Who do you think I am?

09:17.960 --> 09:19.760
Now eat. Then go to work.

09:30.080 --> 09:31.400
- Can I ask you a question?
- Go ahead.

09:31.480 --> 09:33.000
Where did I kiss you?

09:47.880 --> 09:50.320
It's not the first time
I sleepwalked in front of him.

09:50.880 --> 09:52.360
Given the previous experience,

09:52.440 --> 09:54.200
he should have pushed me away.

10:11.400 --> 10:13.120
This is our cutting room.

10:13.200 --> 10:15.880
In the future, if you want to use
the equipment in the cutting room,

10:15.960 --> 10:17.080
you need to report in advance.

10:17.160 --> 10:18.840
Of course, it's okay to sneak in

10:18.920 --> 10:20.880
- if no one's around.
- Okay.

10:20.960 --> 10:23.240
This is Wen Yifan from team C.

10:25.320 --> 10:26.320
What's up, madam?

10:26.840 --> 10:28.000
There are two new interns.

10:31.920 --> 10:33.400
Senior, how are you? I'm Mu Chengyun,

10:33.480 --> 10:34.440
the new intern.

10:36.560 --> 10:38.520
Why do you call her Senior?

10:38.600 --> 10:40.000
Just call her Yifan.

10:40.080 --> 10:42.040
If you call her senior,
who knows who you're calling?

10:42.600 --> 10:44.280
Mu Chengyun.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.200
Give me a hug.

10:46.280 --> 10:47.760
Long time no see.

10:48.520 --> 10:50.080
He's my schoolmate, you know?

10:50.160 --> 10:52.120
And he was a child star when he was young.

10:52.200 --> 10:53.440
Have you watched his movies?

10:53.520 --> 10:54.480
No, I haven't.

10:54.560 --> 10:56.800
What movie? Let me see if I've watched it.

10:57.440 --> 10:58.400
It was like…

10:59.080 --> 11:01.160
- Waking up blah blah blah.
- Waking up to Ghosts.

11:01.240 --> 11:02.440
Yeah, that's it.

11:02.520 --> 11:04.840
I didn't realize Yifan was a fan of mine.

11:05.760 --> 11:07.000
I just know that.

11:07.080 --> 11:08.080
Well, I'll have to check it out.

11:09.080 --> 11:11.200
By the way. My name is Fang Li.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.880
Senior, I'll call you Yifan from now on.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.280
Let me have your WeChat, Chengyun.

11:17.320 --> 11:19.160
- Okay.
- Right. Bring them into the work group.

11:19.240 --> 11:20.080
- Right.
- Work group. Come on.

11:20.160 --> 11:21.600
Bring them into the work group.

11:21.680 --> 11:22.600
Let me tell you about the do's

11:22.680 --> 11:24.320
and don'ts of the work group.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.600
Let's go eat after work.

11:28.120 --> 11:30.480
Okay. Let me show you that place.

11:30.560 --> 11:32.160
- Get familiar with the work environment.
- Okay.

11:32.240 --> 11:33.920
- Come on.
- This way.

11:35.680 --> 11:36.600
SORRY. IT WON'T TAKE LONG

11:36.680 --> 11:39.640
This room is for small conferences.

11:39.720 --> 11:42.440
And up ahead is our call center.

11:42.520 --> 11:44.000
SANG YAN

11:44.080 --> 11:46.720
The call center
has to be staffed 24 hours a day

11:46.800 --> 11:48.360
because we have to take calls at any time.

11:48.440 --> 11:49.400
Everyone, take a look.

11:49.480 --> 11:51.480
These are the two new interns.

11:57.520 --> 11:58.920
TEENAGE PASSER-BY SAVES THE DAY

12:05.880 --> 12:06.720
Yifan.

12:07.760 --> 12:09.240
Am I interrupting?

12:19.400 --> 12:20.240
That's…

12:22.640 --> 12:28.080
￥40,000.00. PLEASE TAKE IT

12:28.680 --> 12:30.160
Isn't that four zeros?

12:30.240 --> 12:31.520
Why so much?

12:36.520 --> 12:40.840
DID YOU TRANSFER TOO MUCH MONEY TO ME?

12:42.760 --> 12:45.120
WHAT? OH. I PUT IN AN EXTRA ZERO

12:48.880 --> 12:50.800
I'LL TRANSFER IT BACK TO YOU

12:52.040 --> 12:53.640
NO NEED. I'LL JUST PAY THE RENT IN ADVANCE

12:54.480 --> 12:55.720
In advance?

12:56.960 --> 12:58.440
Are you staying long?

13:00.080 --> 13:03.160
How many months are you staying?

13:10.440 --> 13:11.360
Thank you.

13:12.480 --> 13:13.720
PRESS TO SPEAK

13:25.800 --> 13:27.600
I didn't mean anything by it.

13:29.040 --> 13:31.320
I just wanted to make sure.

13:31.400 --> 13:34.160
So I know when I can start
looking for a new roommate.

13:35.840 --> 13:38.040
I'll stay until you
pay off your debt to me.

13:39.360 --> 13:40.320
What debt?

13:40.400 --> 13:42.880
What? Do I have to remind you?

13:45.360 --> 13:48.240
Your sanity was overpowered
by desire late at night

13:48.320 --> 13:49.440
and you attempted to possess me.

13:54.280 --> 13:55.800
What?

13:59.080 --> 14:00.000
Yifan.

14:02.320 --> 14:04.040
I just saw that you've been
replying to messages,

14:04.120 --> 14:05.920
so I was wondering
if you're in some kind of trouble.

14:06.000 --> 14:08.640
- Tell me. I can help you.
- I'm not. Thanks.

14:09.320 --> 14:11.400
I have a lot of questions
I want to ask you later.

14:12.000 --> 14:13.880
I'll teach you later.

14:15.640 --> 14:18.240
Anyway, from today onwards,
I'm going to haunt you.

14:20.000 --> 14:21.080
Why?

14:21.160 --> 14:24.160
They asked me to learn from you

14:25.400 --> 14:26.240
during my internship.

14:30.280 --> 14:34.080
Now we're down
to "New House Near Cemetery"

14:34.160 --> 14:38.200
and "Pathetic Mother Searches
For Daughter Who Disappeared".

14:38.280 --> 14:39.200
YOUR SANITY WAS OVERPOWERED
BY DESIRE LATE AT NIGHT

14:39.280 --> 14:41.040
Wang Jing. Yifan.

14:41.120 --> 14:42.800
You two can choose one each.

14:42.880 --> 14:44.040
I'm fine with both,

14:44.720 --> 14:47.080
but Yifan, you're afraid of ghosts,

14:47.880 --> 14:49.360
so I'll take the cemetery one.

14:51.320 --> 14:52.160
I can do both.

14:52.240 --> 14:54.040
Okay. Then, it's settled.

14:55.920 --> 14:57.760
Obviously, she wanted to pick a topic
that would attract attention,

14:57.840 --> 15:00.120
but why did she use your fear
of ghosts as the reason?

15:01.120 --> 15:01.960
Yifan.

15:02.040 --> 15:04.040
Why don't you fight for that news
about the cemetery?

15:04.120 --> 15:06.640
It seemed more topical.

15:07.160 --> 15:10.040
Or do you have no desire
at all to choose a topic?

15:10.600 --> 15:11.440
It's all the same to me.

15:15.280 --> 15:17.280
A mother looking for her daughter.

15:17.360 --> 15:19.200
Looks like we'll have
to make it a touching story.

15:19.280 --> 15:21.560
Let's try to figure out
where her daughter might have gone.

15:21.640 --> 15:24.920
It's a needle in a haystack.
Arduous but fruitless.

15:30.320 --> 15:32.040
You're new here.

15:32.120 --> 15:33.840
Don't be so calculating.

15:38.760 --> 15:41.920
Or, if I find her,

15:42.520 --> 15:43.720
Yifan, can you reward me?

15:46.880 --> 15:49.640
A reward for passing the art exam.

15:50.760 --> 15:53.320
Will you give me a reward if I

15:54.040 --> 15:55.040
overachieve in the college entrance exam?

15:57.040 --> 15:59.560
Let's talk about it after that.

16:00.800 --> 16:02.120
We can't exchange like that.

16:04.560 --> 16:05.800
Maybe we can.

16:06.640 --> 16:07.480
Do you want it?

16:08.680 --> 16:09.520
I've had it.

16:16.160 --> 16:18.080
Good. That's enough for today.

16:18.160 --> 16:19.040
Get to work.

16:28.400 --> 16:29.480
- Don't forget it.
- Okay.

16:39.360 --> 16:40.360
Yifan.

16:40.440 --> 16:42.120
I'll get the equipment.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.600
Anyway, I'll follow you all day today.

16:44.800 --> 16:45.960
Come on, Mu Chengyun.

16:46.040 --> 16:47.120
I'll take you to get the equipment

16:47.200 --> 16:48.840
- and show you how to organize it.
- Okay.

16:54.480 --> 16:56.800
- Cute, right?
- Who?

16:58.000 --> 16:59.400
That guy. Yifan.

17:01.920 --> 17:03.440
ARE YOU OKAY?

17:11.839 --> 17:14.760
HOW DO YOU WANT THIS RESOLVED?

17:23.280 --> 17:26.359
SANG YAN

17:26.960 --> 17:27.960
Hello?

17:28.040 --> 17:29.680
How do you want this resolved?

17:30.760 --> 17:32.560
- Huh?
- Huh what?

17:34.600 --> 17:36.400
Forget it. Talk about it later.

17:36.480 --> 17:38.200
You seem to have
been thinking for a long time.

17:38.280 --> 17:39.360
Yes.

17:39.440 --> 17:42.160
- Then keep thinking.
- Are you in a hurry?

17:43.240 --> 17:44.520
Why should I be?

17:45.200 --> 17:46.640
I'm afraid

17:47.560 --> 17:48.720
you won't be able to control your desire.

17:59.360 --> 18:02.240
When did you lose contact with her?

18:02.960 --> 18:04.560
Last Chinese New Year's Eve.

18:05.160 --> 18:06.240
At first, she transferred money

18:06.760 --> 18:08.280
to me every month,

18:08.960 --> 18:10.920
but from the end of the year, she stopped.

18:12.000 --> 18:13.920
I'm anxious every day.

18:14.000 --> 18:14.840
MISSING PERSON NOTICE

18:14.920 --> 18:17.360
Look at my leg. It's hurt like this.

18:18.120 --> 18:20.360
Sweetheart. If you can see it,

18:20.960 --> 18:22.520
contact me

18:23.320 --> 18:24.840
and give me a message, okay?

18:24.920 --> 18:26.320
For those of you in front of the screen…

18:26.400 --> 18:28.920
- That's it.
- Thank you.

18:30.360 --> 18:31.440
Did you find her?

18:32.160 --> 18:34.520
Neighbors say
they haven't seen her for a week.

18:34.600 --> 18:35.600
This kind of topic is the most dreadful.

18:35.680 --> 18:37.120
It's time-consuming
and hard to get results.

18:37.200 --> 18:38.760
Yifan. I found her.

18:38.840 --> 18:40.960
The mother is not in Nanwu.

18:41.040 --> 18:42.800
She went to Yihe to look for her daughter.

18:42.880 --> 18:44.600
- How do you know?
- The mother

18:44.680 --> 18:46.080
went from Nanwu to the place

18:46.160 --> 18:48.480
where her daughter used to live
in Yihe and held a sign.

18:48.560 --> 18:50.960
Then it happened
to be reported in Yihe Daily.

18:51.040 --> 18:53.120
It seems we have to go to Yihe.

18:53.680 --> 18:54.800
Yihe?

19:15.360 --> 19:16.320
Yifan.

19:16.920 --> 19:19.400
I've prepared everything for the trip.

19:20.120 --> 19:21.040
See if there's anything I'm missing.

19:21.640 --> 19:23.680
- Let me know.
- Thank you.

19:29.120 --> 19:31.000
Yifan, Chengyun. I have to go now. Bye.

19:31.080 --> 19:31.920
- Okay.
- Bye.

19:32.000 --> 19:33.720
- Be safe.
- Okay.

19:36.600 --> 19:38.760
And I just ordered some pizza.

19:38.840 --> 19:39.840
Do you want to eat it while it's hot?

19:41.040 --> 19:41.920
No, thank you.

19:43.560 --> 19:44.520
You don't like it?

19:49.800 --> 19:50.760
Just enjoy it.

20:28.840 --> 20:29.720
You can leave now.

20:31.760 --> 20:33.840
It's okay. I'll stay with you.

20:34.720 --> 20:35.760
We can leave together.

20:35.840 --> 20:37.880
You don't have to.
I'm meeting a friend for dinner.

20:55.880 --> 20:56.800
Dian.

20:59.200 --> 21:00.560
- Let's go.
- Here you go.

21:01.720 --> 21:04.880
Hello. I'm Yifan's exclusive intern,
Mu Chengyun.

21:07.040 --> 21:08.160
Want to get on, handsome?

21:08.240 --> 21:09.400
Stop it.

21:11.080 --> 21:11.960
I'm just kidding.

21:12.040 --> 21:12.880
Let's have dinner sometime.

21:12.960 --> 21:14.080
Okay.

21:14.160 --> 21:15.200
- Bye.
- Bye, Yifan.

21:15.280 --> 21:16.600
Bye.

21:28.840 --> 21:31.480
I think that guy is interested in you.

21:31.560 --> 21:33.200
Stop kidding.

21:33.280 --> 21:34.920
He's just more active at work.

21:35.000 --> 21:36.280
A man and a woman

21:36.360 --> 21:38.200
working overtime in the same room…

21:38.280 --> 21:40.160
With a little catalyst,

21:40.840 --> 21:42.240
he'd be instantly enamored with you.

21:42.880 --> 21:44.800
You seem to know well.

21:45.640 --> 21:46.480
Why don't you drink?

21:46.560 --> 21:48.600
Me? I don't drink alcohol.

21:58.280 --> 22:00.080
Actually, I want

22:00.680 --> 22:02.200
to ask you a favor today.

22:02.280 --> 22:03.560
What?

22:06.200 --> 22:07.520
Do you want me to help you

22:07.600 --> 22:09.360
get rid of that cute handsome guy?

22:09.440 --> 22:10.920
I can do that.

22:11.000 --> 22:12.320
I was wondering

22:12.400 --> 22:15.320
if you had time to come over
and stay with me tonight.

22:18.880 --> 22:20.000
What's wrong with you?

22:20.080 --> 22:21.560
Did Sang Yan bully you?

22:21.640 --> 22:23.760
Did he hit you or abuse you?
Did he do anything else?

22:23.840 --> 22:25.280
No.

22:25.360 --> 22:26.960
Then, what's wrong with you?

22:29.000 --> 22:30.600
I seemed to be sleepwalking.

22:30.680 --> 22:31.600
Sleepwalking?

22:32.440 --> 22:34.280
You haven't mentioned it before.

22:35.160 --> 22:38.720
Actually, I used to
and haven't for a long time,

22:38.800 --> 22:41.440
but lately, it seems
to have started again.

22:42.240 --> 22:44.000
Just maybe.

22:44.760 --> 22:47.200
So, how do you know?

22:47.280 --> 22:48.200
Sang Yan told me.

22:49.720 --> 22:51.280
Did he see it?

22:52.480 --> 22:53.320
Probably.

22:53.400 --> 22:55.560
So, you don't remember what you did
when you were sleepwalking?

22:55.640 --> 22:58.200
Since it was sleepwalking,
I surely don't remember.

22:59.400 --> 23:01.520
Did Sang Yan say what you did?

23:02.040 --> 23:04.920
Your sanity was overpowered
by desire late at night

23:05.000 --> 23:06.120
and you attempted to possess me.

23:06.800 --> 23:09.800
Anyway, tonight, sleep with me
and check for me

23:09.880 --> 23:11.800
if I'm sleepwalking again, okay?

23:11.880 --> 23:13.320
Okay. Don't worry.

23:13.400 --> 23:14.680
I'll definitely take care of you.

23:15.200 --> 23:19.920
So, to sleep better,
let's get a little drunk.

23:20.000 --> 23:20.840
Okay.

23:22.480 --> 23:24.320
Let's go. Let's take a cab home.

23:30.520 --> 23:31.440
Peeled.

23:38.960 --> 23:42.080
I guess I'm the only one who still keeps
the promise to be home by ten.

23:42.160 --> 23:44.320
Is he afraid to come back
because you're sleepwalking?

23:45.200 --> 23:46.040
It's enough that you're not afraid.

23:47.160 --> 23:50.160
- Why would I be?
- If I suddenly open my eyes

23:50.240 --> 23:51.880
and sit up at night, just punch me.

23:53.320 --> 23:55.280
How can I do that do you?

23:55.360 --> 23:57.000
Don't worry. I'm a light sleeper.

23:57.080 --> 23:59.200
When I'm at home, even my dad's snoring
and my brother's teeth grinding

23:59.280 --> 24:00.120
can wake me up.

24:01.280 --> 24:03.440
- Then, I'm counting on you.
- Sit here.

24:08.440 --> 24:10.440
- Are you sleepy?
- I'm not.

24:17.960 --> 24:19.120
He's not back yet.

24:36.640 --> 24:37.840
You're back.

24:44.600 --> 24:45.680
Why you?

24:48.440 --> 24:49.840
I'm sorry.

24:53.680 --> 24:55.800
Are you still up?

25:02.440 --> 25:04.600
I sent you a message. Didn't you get it?

25:06.320 --> 25:09.120
We've been together,
so I didn't notice that.

25:16.080 --> 25:17.960
So, go ahead.

25:21.000 --> 25:22.160
I'll stop interrupting.

25:28.760 --> 25:29.600
So,

25:30.520 --> 25:31.960
it's her who took
liberties with you, right?

25:32.840 --> 25:33.920
Cut the crap.

25:35.320 --> 25:37.400
- Watch yourself.
- I have a feeling it's her.

25:39.840 --> 25:40.880
Right?

25:41.520 --> 25:43.160
No wonder you agreed
to let me live in your house.

25:44.080 --> 25:45.400
You want me to protect you.

25:45.480 --> 25:49.480
WEN YIFAN: QIAO WILL STAY HERE TONIGHT

26:15.560 --> 26:16.760
So, why didn't you tell me in advance

26:16.840 --> 26:18.400
that he was coming last night?

26:22.560 --> 26:24.080
I had nowhere else to go yesterday,

26:24.160 --> 26:25.000
so I could only ask him for help.

26:25.640 --> 26:27.880
I had to find a way to protect myself.

26:38.600 --> 26:39.440
Protect yourself?

26:43.520 --> 26:44.520
What does that mean?

26:45.200 --> 26:46.040
Are you overthinking this?

26:56.200 --> 26:58.200
- Are you overthinking it too?
- I'm not.

27:03.200 --> 27:05.600
So, did you guys sleep well last night?

27:07.440 --> 27:09.280
How could I sleep well
with this guy around?

27:10.240 --> 27:11.160
You didn't sleep well last night?

27:11.240 --> 27:12.400
Of course not.

27:12.480 --> 27:13.840
Never mind.

27:13.920 --> 27:15.720
As long as you guys had fun.

27:16.840 --> 27:18.680
What about you? Did you sleep well?

27:18.760 --> 27:20.960
I'm sure we did.

27:22.880 --> 27:24.000
I hope I didn't disturb you.

27:28.800 --> 27:30.200
It was an interesting meal.

27:30.280 --> 27:33.240
- How interesting can a meal be?
- You are interesting, too.

27:34.200 --> 27:35.080
So are you.

27:35.160 --> 27:36.120
So are you.

27:36.720 --> 27:37.720
Are you done?

27:43.760 --> 27:46.320
By the way, I'm not coming back tonight,

27:46.840 --> 27:48.000
so you can be

27:49.960 --> 27:51.160
more comfortable.

27:52.080 --> 27:54.240
- Where are you going?
- Yihe.

27:57.040 --> 27:59.320
- To do what?
- On a business trip.

28:04.280 --> 28:08.240
YIHE

28:08.320 --> 28:11.360
The willows here
look like snowflakes. Yifan.

28:11.440 --> 28:12.640
You're so predictable.

28:12.720 --> 28:16.080
I wouldn't even be able to breathe
if you hadn't given me that mask.

28:16.160 --> 28:17.760
I lived here for a while.

28:29.000 --> 28:30.800
Hello. How many of you are there?

28:30.880 --> 28:32.120
We're here to see someone. Thank you.

28:35.920 --> 28:36.760
This way.

28:39.200 --> 28:40.840
How are you?
We're reporters from First News.

28:40.920 --> 28:42.920
I'm Wen Yifan. Sorry to keep you waiting.

28:43.640 --> 28:44.680
Thank you for helping me.

28:44.760 --> 28:46.840
My daughter is at your age.

28:47.760 --> 28:48.880
You're welcome.

28:48.960 --> 28:50.240
Have a seat.

29:03.160 --> 29:04.000
We can start.

29:06.840 --> 29:08.480
My daughter graduated from college

29:08.560 --> 29:10.400
and then went to work in Yihe.

29:10.920 --> 29:12.600
For five years, she worked,

29:12.680 --> 29:14.880
she gave me some money every month,

29:15.720 --> 29:17.760
but just before New Year's,

29:17.840 --> 29:19.080
we suddenly lost contact.

29:20.360 --> 29:22.400
Neither during the New Year
nor during the holidays,

29:22.480 --> 29:24.000
she didn't send me a single message

29:24.720 --> 29:26.120
or give me the money she was supposed to.

29:28.160 --> 29:30.920
What is the money she is supposed to give?

29:33.160 --> 29:36.080
It's only natural for a daughter
to take care of her mother.

29:37.040 --> 29:38.360
I'm worried something

29:39.040 --> 29:40.520
might have happened to her.

29:42.320 --> 29:43.360
Sweetheart.

29:44.400 --> 29:46.600
If you see me on TV,

29:47.360 --> 29:50.400
call me back
and tell me you're okay, okay?

29:51.480 --> 29:53.600
How are you getting along
with your daughter?

29:53.680 --> 29:55.240
Have you had any conflicts
or anything like that?

29:57.240 --> 30:01.160
What mother in this world
would treat her daughter badly?

30:01.840 --> 30:05.320
I lost my husband and my job

30:05.400 --> 30:06.920
to raise her.

30:07.000 --> 30:09.480
How can she treat me like this?

30:10.080 --> 30:10.920
Hello?

30:11.000 --> 30:13.320
- Can we talk, Jiang?
- Go ahead.

30:13.400 --> 30:15.320
Is it cold in Yihe?

30:15.400 --> 30:18.080
Remember to eat well
and put on some clothes.

30:19.440 --> 30:21.320
You haven't called me for a while.

30:22.360 --> 30:23.560
I've been too busy lately.

30:23.640 --> 30:25.320
I know you're busy,

30:25.400 --> 30:27.880
so I didn't dare to call and bother you.

30:29.480 --> 30:31.040
How will you

30:32.680 --> 30:34.400
settle Yifan down?

30:36.400 --> 30:40.520
Can you let her stay at your place?

30:40.600 --> 30:42.160
Or let her go to her grandma's.

30:42.240 --> 30:43.760
After all, that's her grandmother,
don't you think?

30:45.880 --> 30:47.520
Think about it. Am I right?

30:52.200 --> 30:54.520
Jiang. I know you blame me.

30:55.720 --> 30:56.720
After your dad died,

30:56.800 --> 30:59.200
I didn't fulfill my duty as a mother.

30:59.280 --> 31:00.320
You can say whatever you want,

31:00.400 --> 31:01.560
but can you not mention my dad?

31:02.320 --> 31:04.400
These days, I've been
dreaming about your dad.

31:05.080 --> 31:06.400
He still blames me.

31:11.520 --> 31:12.840
It's okay. Don't cry.

31:12.920 --> 31:14.440
I'm fine. Don't worry.

31:14.520 --> 31:16.160
I'll come to you when I have time.

31:16.240 --> 31:17.200
See you.

31:21.760 --> 31:24.320
Don't worry. We'll do our best
to find your daughter.

31:25.040 --> 31:26.320
Please keep your word.

31:35.600 --> 31:37.520
It's too suffocating.

31:38.160 --> 31:40.080
Yihe's spring is just like that.

31:40.160 --> 31:41.680
I'm talking about the mother.

31:42.200 --> 31:44.160
That kind of motherhood is suffocating.

31:44.680 --> 31:46.960
Why didn't you ask further just now?

31:47.040 --> 31:50.280
I think there's a reason
her daughter doesn't want to see her.

31:51.200 --> 31:53.280
She doesn't think she has any problems.

31:53.360 --> 31:56.080
Right. She's just pushing
her daughter with affection.

31:57.160 --> 31:59.720
Maybe that's why her daughter disappeared.

31:59.800 --> 32:00.960
How do you know?

32:03.880 --> 32:05.000
The flight is tomorrow.

32:05.080 --> 32:06.600
We're free for the rest of the day.

32:06.680 --> 32:08.720
- Aren't you coming with me?
- No.

32:09.400 --> 32:12.240
Haven't you lived here before?
Show me around.

32:17.520 --> 32:19.400
- Hey, Tian.
- We found her.

32:19.480 --> 32:20.760
Her daughter is in Hong Kong, China.

32:20.840 --> 32:22.360
She's currently working
as an admin at a dance studio.

32:23.000 --> 32:23.840
Okay. I got it.

32:26.240 --> 32:27.480
What's going on?

32:27.560 --> 32:29.040
Did you bring your EEP?

32:30.080 --> 32:31.640
- And the endorsement?
- Yes.

32:31.720 --> 32:33.080
We have to bring
all the documents when we travel.

32:33.160 --> 32:34.120
They taught me all that in training.

32:36.440 --> 32:37.640
Where are we going?

32:37.720 --> 32:39.160
Hong Kong, China.

32:40.640 --> 32:42.880
So, I'll be a day late.

32:45.440 --> 32:46.480
Okay.

32:47.080 --> 32:48.840
- Then--
- Yifan, your card.

32:48.920 --> 32:50.160
Okay. Thank you.

32:51.320 --> 32:52.160
Who's that?

32:53.400 --> 32:54.520
A coworker I came with.

32:54.600 --> 32:56.920
Sounds like a kid.

32:58.960 --> 33:01.880
That's the guy you saw in front
of the supermarket last time.

33:01.960 --> 33:03.360
He's now doing an internship in our group.

33:06.520 --> 33:07.560
Don't you have an umbrella?

33:07.640 --> 33:08.880
Do you want me to take you home?

33:10.600 --> 33:12.680
We have umbrellas. You can leave now.

33:13.320 --> 33:14.760
Are you jealous of me?

33:15.360 --> 33:17.360
Jealous of you? I don't need to be.

33:18.080 --> 33:19.120
Take it.

33:20.520 --> 33:21.480
No.

33:30.240 --> 33:34.680
HONG KONG, CHINA

33:46.280 --> 33:47.120
Let's go.

33:53.320 --> 33:54.240
I'm starving.

33:54.320 --> 33:55.680
- Maybe here.
- Let's go buy something to eat.

33:56.680 --> 33:57.600
I'm not hungry.

33:58.720 --> 34:00.080
OK. I'll order takeout.

34:03.360 --> 34:05.400
Hello. Are you here to enroll?

34:05.480 --> 34:07.240
Please fill out
the form for the adult class.

34:07.920 --> 34:09.920
Couples can get 20% off.

34:10.600 --> 34:12.360
Hello, sir.
We are reporters from First News

34:12.440 --> 34:13.320
of Nanwu TV Station.

34:13.400 --> 34:14.679
- I'm Wen Yifan.
- Mu Chengyun.

34:15.440 --> 34:16.280
I'd like to ask.

34:16.360 --> 34:19.000
Is there a Ms. Lin Yuqing here?

34:20.199 --> 34:22.360
I'm sorry.
We don't have anyone named Lin here.

34:23.560 --> 34:24.440
Then I'd like to ask

34:24.520 --> 34:26.360
if there are any other
dance studios in this building.

34:27.840 --> 34:29.080
I'm not sure.

34:29.159 --> 34:31.040
You can ask somewhere else.

34:34.800 --> 34:36.320
Is there anything else?

34:36.400 --> 34:37.639
If not, I'll get back to work.

34:38.960 --> 34:40.000
Thank you.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.480
What now?

35:02.560 --> 35:03.760
Find another way

35:03.840 --> 35:06.320
or see if there's anyone who knows her?

35:07.040 --> 35:08.040
Wait a little longer.

35:20.360 --> 35:21.480
I've got an idea.

35:26.920 --> 35:28.520
I want to see Ms. Lin Yuqing.

35:29.160 --> 35:31.880
- That's me.
- Here's your takeout.

35:33.560 --> 35:35.800
- Who ordered it?
- I don't know.

35:35.880 --> 35:37.480
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

35:41.400 --> 35:42.920
I just heard you hadn't had lunch yet,

35:43.000 --> 35:44.800
so I took the liberty
of ordering one for you.

35:46.240 --> 35:48.320
I'm sorry. I don't do interviews.

35:48.400 --> 35:50.240
We just want to talk to you.

35:52.760 --> 35:53.800
Don't worry.

35:53.880 --> 35:55.000
Your mother doesn't know we're coming.

36:07.000 --> 36:09.240
You can turn on your cell phone's camera.

36:19.160 --> 36:22.360
I'm happy now and have a family of my own.

36:22.960 --> 36:25.440
I'm asking you
to stop trying to find me, okay?

36:26.080 --> 36:28.240
Okay. Show her this video.

36:30.880 --> 36:33.120
Is there anything else you want to say?

36:34.720 --> 36:36.200
What should I say?

36:37.600 --> 36:39.240
Should I tell onlookers

36:39.320 --> 36:42.120
that she married a man and had a child

36:42.720 --> 36:44.240
or that she realized

36:44.800 --> 36:48.040
she had a daughter
after he disappeared with her son

36:48.680 --> 36:50.280
and abandoned her,

36:51.360 --> 36:52.560
or should I tearfully

36:52.640 --> 36:54.840
accuse her of using
her affection to blackmail me

36:54.920 --> 36:56.560
and treating me as her property

36:56.640 --> 36:58.960
in order to receive
monthly maintenance from me?

37:01.120 --> 37:02.480
I can understand you.

37:07.560 --> 37:08.960
How can you understand me?

37:09.880 --> 37:10.760
You're not me.

37:12.160 --> 37:13.640
My mother was a lot like her,

37:14.640 --> 37:18.280
but she didn't look for me or care for me

37:18.360 --> 37:19.560
when I left Nanwu.

37:20.120 --> 37:21.480
So, if it were you,

37:22.400 --> 37:23.440
would you forgive her?

37:24.360 --> 37:25.280
No.

37:27.240 --> 37:28.280
At least not now.

37:34.680 --> 37:36.320
I don't want you to go back with nothing,

37:37.040 --> 37:40.000
so show her that video.

37:51.440 --> 37:52.760
Go back.

37:58.040 --> 37:59.560
What's wrong?

37:59.640 --> 38:01.480
I'm fine. I just can't handle them.

38:02.560 --> 38:04.320
How can't you? They're cute.

38:04.400 --> 38:05.800
I'll go see them.

38:08.000 --> 38:08.880
Come on.

38:08.960 --> 38:10.280
The kids.

38:10.360 --> 38:11.720
He says he can't handle you.

38:11.800 --> 38:13.160
What's going on?

38:13.920 --> 38:15.840
Sit down. Sit down.

38:16.440 --> 38:17.480
What's going on?

38:18.160 --> 38:19.320
Isabella.

38:21.720 --> 38:22.840
What's wrong with you?

38:23.840 --> 38:24.840
I'm so stupid.

38:24.920 --> 38:26.640
I can't even do it.

38:26.720 --> 38:28.440
I was spinning until I was dizzy.

38:29.240 --> 38:30.240
What's going on?

38:30.320 --> 38:33.240
It's just hard.

38:33.320 --> 38:36.440
Listen. Stand up and show me
which move that was.

38:43.240 --> 38:44.280
Are you tired?

38:44.360 --> 38:45.560
Then, let's take a break.

38:45.640 --> 38:46.720
You'll be fine with more practice later.

39:01.280 --> 39:02.920
Your name is Isabella, right?

39:03.640 --> 39:04.720
You just did a great job,

39:04.800 --> 39:07.520
but there's a little problem
you should pay attention to.

39:07.600 --> 39:09.280
When you do the movements…
Come on. Stand up.

39:12.080 --> 39:13.080
When you do the movement,

39:13.160 --> 39:15.200
center your weight in this area.

39:15.280 --> 39:17.480
We must not look at the ground

39:17.560 --> 39:19.360
but ahead. Forward.

39:20.040 --> 39:21.080
OK?

39:21.160 --> 39:22.920
I'll show you how it's done.

39:35.720 --> 39:37.760
You don't seem so happy for a long time.

39:41.280 --> 39:42.960
Come on. Try it.

39:46.760 --> 39:48.800
Sir, can you do me a favor?

39:48.880 --> 39:51.000
Let's just stare at this teacher.

39:51.080 --> 39:52.080
Look straight at him.

39:52.160 --> 39:53.560
Keep looking at him, okay?

39:54.120 --> 39:54.960
Straighten up.

39:55.040 --> 39:56.240
Come on. Try it.

40:00.920 --> 40:02.120
That's good.

40:03.440 --> 40:04.720
Did you get it?

40:05.360 --> 40:08.360
- Miss, you're great.
- So are you.

40:08.960 --> 40:11.080
When you dance, you have to relax.
Having fun is the most important thing,

40:11.160 --> 40:12.720
right?

40:12.800 --> 40:14.080
You're not dizzy anymore, right?

40:15.080 --> 40:16.600
Excuse me.

40:16.680 --> 40:18.120
Are you a dance teacher?

40:18.200 --> 40:19.320
No, I'm not.

40:20.200 --> 40:21.320
We should probably get going.

40:22.080 --> 40:23.120
Thank you very much.

40:25.120 --> 40:26.200
Come on.

40:27.560 --> 40:29.360
- Say goodbye to them.
- Bye.

40:29.440 --> 40:30.360
Bye.

40:30.440 --> 40:31.440
- Bye.
- Bye.

40:32.880 --> 40:33.840
Thanks.

40:36.680 --> 40:38.120
Come on. Let's go.
Let's get on with the lesson.

40:38.200 --> 40:41.800
Go on.

40:53.040 --> 40:54.440
Chengyun, I'm here.

40:55.000 --> 40:56.680
Didn't I tell you not to pick me up?

40:56.760 --> 40:58.120
I'm not a kid.

40:58.200 --> 40:59.200
Brat.

40:59.280 --> 41:00.800
Grandpa's birthday is today,

41:00.880 --> 41:02.800
so how could I not pick you up myself?

41:02.880 --> 41:03.960
Oh…

41:04.040 --> 41:06.280
Yifan. Let me introduce you.
This is my sister.

41:06.360 --> 41:07.880
- How are you?
- Hi.

41:07.960 --> 41:09.840
I've heard a lot about you
from my brother.

41:09.920 --> 41:11.840
He's always giving you trouble, isn't he?

41:15.240 --> 41:16.920
By the way, is someone
coming to pick you up?

41:17.760 --> 41:18.960
I don't usually have that.

41:19.600 --> 41:21.800
Come on, then. We'll take you home.

41:21.880 --> 41:23.440
Yes. Come with us.

41:23.520 --> 41:25.440
- I can take a cab.
- Wen Yifan.

41:27.400 --> 41:28.680
Why are you here?

41:30.160 --> 41:31.640
I'm seeing a friend off,

41:31.720 --> 41:32.560
so I thought I'd pick you up on the way.

41:33.640 --> 41:35.720
- Such a coincidence.
- Consider it a basic courtesy

41:35.800 --> 41:36.920
from me as a roommate.

41:37.960 --> 41:40.800
Yifan. Is this your roommate
you mentioned?

41:41.400 --> 41:42.440
Yes.

41:43.840 --> 41:44.880
Are you leaving now?

41:46.840 --> 41:47.760
I'm leaving.

41:47.840 --> 41:48.480
- Bye, Yifan.
- OK.

41:48.560 --> 41:49.520
Okay. Thank you.

41:52.200 --> 41:53.440
Let's go.

41:53.520 --> 41:54.920
She's gone. Don't look at her.

41:55.000 --> 41:57.040
This guy looks familiar to me.

41:57.120 --> 41:58.360
I think I've seen him somewhere.

42:11.440 --> 42:13.600
Were you sleepwalking in Hong Kong, China?

42:15.080 --> 42:16.320
No.

42:24.080 --> 42:25.480
How's work going?

42:31.440 --> 42:33.080
I think you may be happy.

42:33.160 --> 42:34.960
You went to Yihe
and then to Hong Kong, China.

42:36.600 --> 42:38.080
Not bad.

42:39.080 --> 42:40.240
What?

42:40.320 --> 42:41.600
You don't look happy.

42:44.000 --> 42:45.080
I wonder if,

42:46.720 --> 42:49.160
as a journalist, I should be more calm

42:49.240 --> 42:51.720
and objective when it comes to my work.

42:52.720 --> 42:55.400
You're a human being,
not an interviewing machine.

42:56.520 --> 42:59.400
However, I'm easily affected
by the interviewee's mood

42:59.480 --> 43:01.360
when working.

43:02.360 --> 43:03.600
Just be yourself.

43:10.520 --> 43:13.840
Didn't you catch up
with your college friends

43:17.280 --> 43:18.480
or hang out in Yihe?

43:20.680 --> 43:22.240
I thought hard about it.

43:22.320 --> 43:23.640
In my four years of college

43:23.720 --> 43:25.720
and two years of internships,

43:25.800 --> 43:27.800
there really wasn't anything
in Yihe that I missed.

43:27.880 --> 43:31.280
It was a place with no memories for me.

43:31.360 --> 43:34.840
Even on many occasions,
I wished I had never been there.

43:35.840 --> 43:37.800
Because of the rumors
about you and the director,

43:37.880 --> 43:39.560
his wife came to cause trouble,
but you never did that,

43:39.640 --> 43:40.760
so why do you care about her?

43:41.360 --> 43:42.280
Are you really afraid of those people

43:42.360 --> 43:44.280
talking about you behind your back?

43:45.320 --> 43:47.640
I didn't do that,
so I'm not afraid of misunderstanding.

43:49.120 --> 43:50.520
Then why do you leave your job?

43:52.520 --> 43:54.840
Because there's nothing left for me here.

43:55.680 --> 43:58.760
Then, will you take a break
or go to another vocation?

43:58.840 --> 44:00.800
By then, you'll meet other male coworkers.

44:00.880 --> 44:01.720
Nanwu.

44:03.400 --> 44:04.960
I suddenly want to go back to Nanwu.

44:13.400 --> 44:16.920
STRAWBERRY SHORTCAKE

44:17.000 --> 44:18.000
When I left,

44:18.800 --> 44:20.720
I couldn't even bring myself

44:20.800 --> 44:22.640
to buy a cake.

44:27.160 --> 44:28.720
I remember you said

44:29.360 --> 44:32.080
the last time you flew was to Yihe.

44:33.040 --> 44:33.880
For what?

45:26.880 --> 45:27.800
I went to see an old friend.

45:50.480 --> 45:51.320
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

45:51.400 --> 45:52.320
Who's that?

45:52.400 --> 45:54.720
Sounds like a kid.

45:54.800 --> 45:57.280
That's the guy you saw in front
of the supermarket last time.

45:57.360 --> 45:59.400
He's now doing an internship in our group.

46:00.640 --> 46:01.640
OK.

46:03.000 --> 46:04.080
Duan Jiaxu.

46:06.200 --> 46:07.320
What's going on?

46:08.400 --> 46:10.640
Have you booked your flight back?

46:12.280 --> 46:13.200
Not yet.

46:14.280 --> 46:15.280
What?

46:19.280 --> 46:21.840
So, how many days
are you going to stay here?

46:25.920 --> 46:28.280
- Maybe…
- Tomorrow. Tomorrow afternoon, okay?

46:28.360 --> 46:29.400
I'll book a flight for you.

46:29.480 --> 46:31.120
What's wrong with me
staying with you for a few days?

46:31.200 --> 46:32.600
Don't you think the whole house lights up

46:32.680 --> 46:34.080
when you come to my place?

46:34.160 --> 46:35.160
I'm glowing.

46:35.240 --> 46:37.360
You're like a huge light bulb.

46:37.440 --> 46:38.320
Just leave.

46:39.520 --> 46:40.680
Tomorrow. Tomorrow afternoon.

46:40.760 --> 46:42.360
I…

46:42.440 --> 46:43.720
What's wrong with me
staying here for a few days?

46:47.000 --> 46:49.040
By the way,
is someone coming to pick you up?

46:49.640 --> 46:51.760
- I don't usually have that.
- Wen Yifan.

46:54.240 --> 46:55.080
Why are you here?

46:55.840 --> 46:57.400
I'm seeing a friend off,

46:57.480 --> 46:58.720
so I thought I'd pick you up on the way.

49:44.560 --> 49:45.640
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

49:45.720 --> 49:46.840
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
